item.title: Issue-1
item.description: NBA NEWS: Some HORSE and 2k going on in the NBA. Devin Booker beat Deandre Ayton in a 2k tournament and Trae Young played Chauncey Billips in HORSE. As you can tell if you watched the video of them playing 2k, Devin Booker was very happy winning. In HORSE, Chauncey did end up winning over Trae Young.

item.title: Issue-2
item.description: NBA NEWS: In the NBA, some sad news came as Karl Anthony-Towns's mother died because of the coronavirus. The Towns family thanked all the workers who tried to keep Karl Anthony-Towns's mother safe. Also, Zach Lavine after a picture with is fiancee got down on one knee in front of is fiancee and got out a ring. So it turns out Zach Lavine and his fiancee are getting married!
